    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2335870/extras/53a01a1b913f71898dcfb7a20b454b62.poster.avif?t=1705083594\" width=600 height=206 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2335870/extras/53a01a1b913f71898dcfb7a20b454b62.webm?t=1705083594\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2335870/extras/53a01a1b913f71898dcfb7a20b454b62.mp4?t=1705083594\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>.<br><br>Immerse yourself in a feline world full of strategy and fun with this exciting card game. Inspired by the classic Triple Triad from Final Fantasy VIII, this experience combines the thrill of battle with the collection of over 100 collectible cards.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2335870/extras/aff2b7f2defbe6ed526bf942477638ec.poster.avif?t=1705083594\" width=600 height=206 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2335870/extras/aff2b7f2defbe6ed526bf942477638ec.webm?t=1705083594\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2335870/extras/aff2b7f2defbe6ed526bf942477638ec.mp4?t=1705083594\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>.<br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Characteristics</h2></strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\">    <li><i>Deck building:</i>  Depending on the different game rules, you can create and modify your decks dynamically.<br>    </li><li><i>Random Levels:</i>  Every time you arrive in a new city, the challenges will change.<br>    </li><li><i>Crazy rules:</i> The fights are managed by a series of rules, these can change depending on the fight.<br>    </li><li><i>Mini games:</i>  Minigames allow you to get new cards and also win some money.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2335870/extras/ea215a3f967bfa1cb7a5a4d6ec15c146.poster.avif?t=1705083594\" width=600 height=206 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2335870/extras/ea215a3f967bfa1cb7a5a4d6ec15c146.webm?t=1705083594\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2335870/extras/ea215a3f967bfa1cb7a5a4d6ec15c146.mp4?t=1705083594\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>.",
